org.gearvrf

Interface GVRAndroidResource.CompressedTextureCallback

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GVRAndroidResource.Callback<GVRTexture>, GVRAndroidResource.CancelableCallback<GVRTexture>, GVRAndroidResource.TextureCallback
    Enclosing class:
    GVRAndroidResource

    public static interface GVRAndroidResource.CompressedTextureCallback
extends GVRAndroidResource.TextureCallback
    Callback for asynchronous compressed-texture loads. Compressed textures load very quickly, so they're not subject to throttling and don't support GVRAndroidResource.CancelableCallback.stillWanted(GVRAndroidResource)
